# Mondial Relay Integration Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR

    User[Search Request]

    Provider[MondialRelayLiveProvider]

    Client[MondialRelayClient]

    SOAP[SOAP Request]

    XML[XML Response]

    Parser[MondialRelayResponseParser]

    Mapper[MondialRelayMapper]

    Model[PickupPointModel]

    User --> Provider

    Provider --> Client

    Client --> SOAP

    SOAP --> XML

    XML --> Parser

    Parser --> Mapper

    Mapper --> Model
```

